name: Tape Measure
description: A standard tape measure is used for all kinds of field measurements

name: Hammer
description: A hammer is used to secure electrical boxes equipped with nail-on brackets to wall studs and other framing members in a home

name: Torpedo Level
description: A small level, such as a torpedo level, fits easily in a tool pouch and is used to make sure your work is level and plumb.

name: Voltmeter
description: A voltmeter is used to read voltage levels and verify that circuits are “live” or off.
